  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8  \u2013 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Tamil Progressive Alliance's decision regarding the presidential election is tomorrow - Mano",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tamil Progressive Alliance leader Mano Ganesan said that the Tamil Progressive Alliance leadership committee will take a decision on the presidential election tomorrow.",
        "The leadership committee of the Tamil Progressive Alliance will meet tomorrow, Tuesday 19th at 06.00 pm at the party secretariat in Colombo.",
        "In this case, Tamil Progressive Alliance President Mano Ganesan has also informed that all the candidates who have submitted their nomination papers to run in the Parliament on the 20th will be discussed and decided."
      ],
